        "heading": "Meet our founders",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Founder_-_Desktop.jpg",
        "details": "<b class=\"fw-500 d-block mb-2\">Purdy Rubin &amp; Charlotte Figg are on a mission to make natural cleaning more effective, more effortless, and more enjoyable.</b>\nFrom a Hertfordshire garage to millions of homes, their multipurpose spray, scented with essential oils, is on the way to changing the way we all feel about cleaning - for good."
